{"tid":733451,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【港姐2018】黃夏蕙契女林昕雨被爆違約　正式宣佈退選","createTime":"2018-07-07T18:02:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-08T06:21:43.000Z","uid":137470,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5e9a01079dbdead8e0242b1b701710d5053fcf70","tid":733451,"uid":137470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T18:02:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1622154/org/395c5dadfda200322023defbf1d9b957.JPG/xq_h8qZfVEDsg6IfEvjGBBE3AT_BjyiZU9vVf1Pb1X8?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1622154%2Forg%2F395c5dadfda200322023defbf1d9b957.JPG%2Fxq_h8qZfVEDsg6IfEvjGBBE3AT_BjyiZU9vVf1Pb1X8%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=8a132f6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有份參加香港小姐競選2018首輪面試的林昕雨，因為其黃夏蕙契女身分而備受關注。不過「亞洲太平洋國際小姐」大會籌委會及主辦單位便在今日（7日）發出聲明，指林昕雨在上月2日與有關單位簽定經理人合約，所以她參選港姐這個行為是違反協議，亦為此保留所有法律權利。林昕雨接受傳媒訪問時便指自己不知道有關聲明，不過都會飲水思源，不繼續參加港姐選舉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/207979/%E6%B8%AF%E5%A7%902018-%E9%BB%83%E5%A4%8F%E8%95%99%E5%A5%91%E5%A5%B3%E6%9E%97%E6%98%95%E9%9B%A8%E8%A2%AB%E7%88%86%E9%81%95%E7%B4%84-%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E5%AE%A3%E4%BD%88%E9%80%80%E9%81%B8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%2F207979%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A7%25902018-%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%25A4%258F%25E8%2595%2599%25E5%25A5%2591%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E6%259E%2597%25E6%2598%2595%25E9%259B%25A8%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E7%2588%2586%25E9%2581%2595%25E7%25B4%2584-%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E5%25BC%258F%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E4%25BD%2588%25E9%2580%2580%25E9%2581%25B8&d=s3HBX4posvzDLP5f%2Fuwbz%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=0db51dad\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/207979/%E6%B8%AF%E5%A7%902018-%E9%BB%83%E5%A4%8F%E8%95%99%E5%A5%91%E5%A5%B3%E6%9E%97%E6%98%95%E9%9B%A8%E8%A2%AB%E7%88%86%E9%81%95%E7%B4%84-%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E5%AE%A3%E4%BD%88%